{
  "texts": [
    "This training process equips the MLP with the knowledge and parameters required to make accurate predictions when presented with novel input data, with its efficacy hinging on meticulous data preparation and the continual refinement of model parameters.",
    "The system of the modified CN is comparable to Hinton's CN.",
    "The convolutional layer, the hidden layer, the PrimaryCaps layer, and the DigitCaps layer are the four layers that make up the CN [50].A capsule is created when the input characteristics are on the lowest layer.",
    "There are several capsules in each stratum of the CN.",
    "The activation layer computes the length of the CN to recompute the feature component scores to train the CN and represents instantiation entity parameters."
  ]
}